{"tid":926835,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"中國歌迷舉牌支持  關家姐唱出16年前出道作！","createTime":"2018-12-03T17:45:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-03T17:45:39.000Z","uid":66923,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"da48a5c9962ffa0a03684f9397a19c900143e6b2","tid":926835,"uid":66923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T17:45:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_KHKP9WJwSk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_KHKP9WJwSk&d=uFkZx1s7nkArXKMgcnoP%2BrZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=be9b17ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_KHKP9WJwSk</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kRTLwH3d0xA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DkRTLwH3d0xA&d=uFkZx1s7nkArXKMgcnoP%2BrZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=9231c3fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kRTLwH3d0xA</a><br />\n關心妍Jade近年減少了幕前工作，專心湊寶貝女心心外，亦兼顧「妍亮生命慈善基金」音樂治療學校的音樂老師，幫助有情緒問題的弱勢社羣。<br />\n隨着女兒慢慢長大，Jade亦開始慢慢復工。<br />\n<img src=\"https://bka.mpweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/2-5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbka.mpweekly.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F12%2F2-5.jpg&h=b1bb251d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n出道時憑一首《負擔不起》橫掃新人獎的Jade，最近就被邀出席內地音樂節目《粵語好聲音2018》擔任評判，身體力行支持廣東歌，大會特別希望她唱出《負擔不起》和《放生》。<br />\n<img src=\"https://bka.mpweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/3-4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbka.mpweekly.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F12%2F3-4.jpg&h=92d34ebd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沒有到內地工作已有一段時間的她，估不到錄影當日來了三十多位歌迷入場舉牌支持，更全場大合唱Jade的出道作，Jade說︰「其實這個節目六年前已找我，但當時檔期未配合到，之後又懷孕生BB，今次終於應邀出席，《負擔不起》是○二年出道的歌曲，已經十六年了，大家仲記得，見到一班內地歌迷好驚喜。」節目於上周六播出，歌迷紛紛留言問Jade何時再開騷？她說︰「開騷就要好好籌備，新歌應該明年會有。」"}]}